channel.title: Barwick Road Baptist Church
channel.description: Barwick Road Church is made up of people just like you. We come from many different cultures, races, and walks of life. We understand that life is full of ups and downs, joys and sorrows. We know that facing it alone is tough, and having someone really care is priceless.
